            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Callicrateae <lb n="2"/>Philesi <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>sacerdoti in <expan><abbr>perpet</abbr><ex>uum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Providentiae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>et Salutis publicae <lb n="6"/>tribules tribus Agripp<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>ae <lb n="7"/>bene meritae
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Identische Weihung für diese Priesterin bei Korinth gefunden (= AE 1971, 442 = 1974, 607 = 1978, 778). (B): Abweichende Textgestaltung am Ende der Z. 6.</p>
            </div>
